name: The CMS Unit Rejected Moves Options page supports selecting options from the menu.
fullName: tests/features/optionMenu.feature#The CMS Unit Rejected Moves Options page supports selecting options from the menu.

steps.name: Given I am logged into the CMS application
When I click the "TrackingMenu" on the "homePage" Page
And I click the "MovementsMenu" on the "homePage" Page
And I click the "UnitRejectedMovesMenu" on the "homePage" Page
And I click the option menu
Then I verified Option menu popup
And I log out from the CMS application
